00:03:13.832 --> 00:03:15.713
four x plus three or we could just write

00:03:15.713 --> 00:03:20.055
x times the quantity four
x plus three squared.

00:03:20.055 --> 00:03:21.888
And so we've just factored it completely,

00:03:21.888 --> 00:03:23.293
