out from all of these terms?

00:03:26.056 --> 00:03:27.936
I could factor out an x
from all of those terms,

00:03:27.936 --> 00:03:30.328
and then to realize what we had left over

00:03:30.328 --> 00:03:33.834
was a perfect square,
really using this pattern

00:03:33.834 --> 00:03:37.858
that we were able to
see in previous videos.

